OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779789944
OL,3,CUrine test for lung cancer 'could be
OL,4,Cready for NHS use in five years'
OL,6,FA simple urine test for lung cancer
OL,7,Fcould be available for NHS use in as
OL,8,Flittle as five years, according to
OL,9,Fexperts.
OL,11,FThe majority of cases of lung cancer
OL,12,Fin England are diagnosed at later
OL,13,Fstages, meaning the disease can be
OL,14,Fharder to treat.
OL,16,FBut the new urine test can indicate
OL,17,Fthe first possible signs of the
OL,18,Fdisease, which could potentially mean
OL,19,Fcancer could be caught earlier and
OL,20,Fallow patients to get treatments
OL,21,Fsooner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
