FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779789944
OL,3,CUrine test for lung cancer 'could be
OL,4,Cready for NHS use in five years'
OL,6,FScientists funded by Cancer Research
OL,7,FUK have now passed another hurdle,
OL,8,Fbringing the test closer to patient
OL,9,Fuse.
OL,11,FWhile more research is still needed in
OL,12,Fthe field, the test could one day be
OL,13,Fused in GP surgeries and hospitals to
OL,14,Fcatch lung cancer much earlier.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
