OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779789944
OL,3,CUrine test for lung cancer 'could be
OL,4,Cready for NHS use in five years'
OL,6,FProfessor Ljiljana Fruk, from the
OL,7,FUniversity of Cambridge, said she
OL,8,Fhopes to see the test "working in real
OL,9,Fpatients and rolled out across the NHS
OL,10,Fwithin the next five years, making a
OL,11,Freal difference to people at risk of
OL,12,Fthis devastating disease".
OL,14,FThe pioneering test looks for so-
OL,15,Fcalled "zombie" cell proteins which
OL,16,Fcould indicate a patient has lung
OL,17,Fcancer in its earliest stages `
OL,18,Fmeaning the disease could be detected
OL,19,Fmonths or even years before symptoms
OL,20,Fappear.
OL,26,@pD@WOUtD@YO]wD@HOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
