FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779789944
OL,3,CUrine test for lung cancer 'could be
OL,4,Cready for NHS use in five years'
OL,6,FScientists at the University of
OL,7,FCambridge's Department of Chemical
OL,8,FEngineering and Biotechnology, and the
OL,9,FEarly Cancer Institute, along with the
OL,10,FCancer Research UK Cambridge Centre
OL,11,FThoracic Cancer Programme and in
OL,12,Fcollaboration with Royal Papworth
OL,13,FHospital NHS Foundation Trust, looked
OL,14,Fat proteins excreted by senescent
OL,15,Fcells.
OL,17,FThese cells are often referred to as
OL,18,F"zombie cells" because they are alive
OL,19,Fin the body but are unable to grow and
OL,20,Fdivide.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779789944
OL,3,CUrine test for lung cancer 'could be
OL,4,Cready for NHS use in five years'
OL,6,FThe cells cause tissue damage by
OL,7,Freprogramming their immediate
OL,8,Fenvironment to help promote the
OL,9,Femergence of cancer cells.
OL,11,FNow, scientists have developed a
OL,12,Fsensor that is injected which
OL,13,Finteracts with zombie cell proteins
OL,14,Fand releases an easily detectable
OL,15,Fcompound into urine, which signals
OL,16,Ftheir presence.
OL,18,FAnd researchers found the urine sensor
OL,19,Fmay also work for detecting other lung
OL,20,Fdiseases such as pulmonary fibrosis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
