FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779789944
OL,3,CUrine test for lung cancer 'could be
OL,4,Cready for NHS use in five years'
OL,6,FCancer Research UK's spokesman for the
OL,7,Feast of England, Patrick Keely, said:
OL,8,F"With new technologies opening doors
OL,9,Fto new discoveries, we're living in a
OL,10,Fgolden age of research, which is
OL,11,Fpowerfully underlined by this
OL,12,Finnovative new urine test to detect
OL,13,Fearly lung cancer."
